Package: libnginx-mod-http-statsd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, nginx | nginx-full | nginx-extras
Description: nginx HTTP statsd module
 This nginx module allows sending statistics to statsd servers.
 .
 The module provides directives to:
  - Set the statsd server address
  - Configure sampling rates
  - Send counters and timing data
  - Conditionally send statistics based on variables
 .
 This is a dynamic module that can be loaded by nginx.
